title: Watch Ibibio Sound Machine Live on KEXP from Seattle's The Triple Door

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Ibibio Sound Machine performing live on KEXP from The Triple Door. Recorded October 10, 2024.

Songs:
Electricity 01:25
The Talking Fish (Asem Usem Iyak) 06:24
The Chant (Iquo Isang) 13:29
Fire 19:35
Protection From Evil 25:13

I Need You To Be Sweet Like Sugar (Nnge Nte Suka) 36:17
All That You Want 42:42

Eno Williams - Vocals
